<h2>THE GENETICS OF PARKINSON'S</h2>
<p class="rfi-pad20b"><a href="https://www.michaeljfox.org/page.html?ppmi-genetics&amp;utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=homepage&amp;utm_content=ppmi&amp;utm_campaign=gppmilaunch&amp;s_src=gppmilaunch&amp;s_subsrc=homepage"><img src="/files/genes.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="160" /></a></p>
<p>Studying the genetics of Parkinson's could revolutionize the development of new treatments for patients worldwide. Families that carry genetic mutations linked to Parkinson's play a unique role in the pursuit of a cure.</p>
